(49, 1, '2018-08-16 10:17:31', '2018-08-16 07:17:31', '<div class=\"top-p \">A modern take on American-style gin. Fresh citrus, familiar juniper and an elegant floral finish create an elevated, highly drinkable gin. Distilled from grapes, bottled at 40% ABV.</div>\r\n          <div class=\"border-box\">\r\n            <div class=\"top-h2 \">Crafted with<br> lazy, cloud<br> gazing in mind</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"top-p \">Curabitur auctor non quam sed sagittis. Aliquam cursus mollis imperdiet. Etiam vel ligula ac lacus iaculis ullamcorper at id felis. Aenean nec hendrerit diam. Phasellus eu diam id purus pharetra pulvinar. Etiam imperdiet magna ut elit vulputate, eget elementum risus tincidunt. Aliquam vulputate nec nunc dapibus pretium. Nam feugiat felis sed odio malesuada, et vestibulum purus consectetur.</div>\r\n          <div class=\"top-p \">Ut molestie dapibus tempus. Nunc sagittis lectus a ornare molestie. Etiam iaculis accumsan nulla aliquet pretium. Aenean risus dolor, pharetra aliquam augue blandit.</div>\r\n          <div class=\"top-p \">Ut molestie dapibus tempus. Nunc sagittis lectus a ornare molestie. Etiam iaculis accumsan nulla aliquet pretium. Aenean risus dolor, pharetra aliquam augue blandit,</div>', 'Suday Gin', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'suday-gin', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:38:03', '2018-08-16 17:38:03', '', 0, 'http://blog.youandyours.com/?post_type=red_book&#038;p=49', 0, 'red_book', '', 0),
